description: Welcome to Trimount Place. Home to 55 delightful dwellings crafted by a top class team. Trimount Place has it all, with two roofdecks, a sky lounge, fitness center, community room, Wi-Fi lounge, pet spa, cool hangout spaces on every floor, and amazing views from sunrise to sunset - we’ve brought an entire neighborhood to your front door. This is what you’ve been waiting for.Pristine Finishes include Samsung Appliance Package, Quartz countertops, custom kitchen cabnitery, white oak engineered hardwood floors, tasteful millwork and plenty more! Experience home ownership in Boston’s fastest changing neighborhood. Are you ready to take the leap?
